    "Why should we believe in P3?",
    "The key reason is that ensuring alignment of AI models, particularly advanced models, is difficult.",
    "First, it seems that superior capacity to achieve goals places few constraints on what the goals of AI models are.",
    "A model can be very intelligent in the sense of being excellent at achieving its goals for almost any set of goals.",
    "foot_3 There is no guarantee that the goals will strike humans as reasonable or ethical."
